{"id":15057,"date":"2024-03-20T16:57:58","date_gmt":"2024-03-20T09:57:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=15057"},"modified":"2024-03-20T16:57:58","modified_gmt":"2024-03-20T09:57:58","slug":"thu-chay-hyundai-venue-hai-hoa-nhat-phan-khuc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/thu-chay-hyundai-venue-hai-hoa-nhat-phan-khuc\/","title":{"rendered":"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"knc-menu-nav\">\n<div id=\"menuNav\" class=\"kmn-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"kmnw-content\">\n<div class=\"kc-item kc-facebook\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"kc-item kc-email\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"w640 fr clear\">\n<h2 class=\"sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\">Hyundai Venue s\u1edf h\u1eefu ngo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh b\u1eaft m\u1eaft th\u1eddi trang, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c vui th\u00fa khi c\u1ea7m l\u00e1i nh\u1edd c\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac<\/h2>\n<div class=\"clearall\"><\/div>\n<div data-check-position=\"body_start\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"contentdetail\">\n<div id=\"mainContent\" class=\"detail-cmain ss\">\n<div class=\"detail-content afcbc-body\" data-role=\"content\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><b>Ngo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1 t\u00ednh<\/b><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16\/12\/2023, Hyundai Venue nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng b\u1edfi ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. Sau 2 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2024, doanh s\u1ed1 m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea1t 293 xe.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-3-1710819883364-17108198834621966474543.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 1.\" src=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-3-1710819883364-17108198834621966474543.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 1.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-3-1710819883364-17108198834621966474543.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-7-1710819884888-1710819885055387546387.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 2.\" src=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-7-1710819884888-1710819885055387546387.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 2.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-7-1710819884888-1710819885055387546387.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hyundai Venue c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t mang \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u1eabu xe \u0111\u00e0n anh Palisade v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh th\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc Cascading Grill theo phong c\u00e1ch Parametric Dynamic. Xe c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 d\u00e0i x r\u1ed9ng x cao l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 3.995 x 1.770 x 1.645 (mm), chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ea1t 2.500 mm, kho\u1ea3ng s\u00e1ng g\u1ea7m 195 (mm). Tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Hyundai Venue l\u00e0\u00a0 g\u1ea7n 1,2 t\u1ea5n.<\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u xe n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng full LED, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ea5u k\u00ednh h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 projector \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao b\u1ecdc trong c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n ban ng\u00e0y LED t\u00edch h\u1ee3p, \u0110\u00e8n xinhan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean tr\u00ean cao.. Ph\u00eda d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 h\u1ed1c gi\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn, vi\u1ec1n \u1ed1p xung quanh t\u0103ng th\u00eam v\u1ebb h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-10-1710819886216-1710819886334711827749.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 3.\" src=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-10-1710819886216-1710819886334711827749.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 3.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-10-1710819886216-1710819886334711827749.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-18-1710819887002-17108198873581642644016.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 4.\" src=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-18-1710819887002-17108198873581642644016.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 4.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-ngoaithat05-18-1710819887002-17108198873581642644016.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">La-z\u0103ng h\u1ee3p kim 5 ch\u1ea5u k\u00e9p m\u1edbi, s\u01a1n hai m\u00e0u, k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc 16 inch \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 l\u1ed1p 215\/60 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n. Nh\u1eefng l\u00f4 xe \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc xe tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1p c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u MRF, kh\u00e1 xa l\u1ea1 \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tuy v\u1eady theo t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u l\u1ed1p n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9.<\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ph\u1ea7n \u0111u\u00f4i xe s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu LED v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf trending hi\u1ec7n nay k\u00e9o ngang \u0111u\u00f4i xe. C\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu mang phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh chi ti\u1ebft d\u1ea1ng pixel t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf xe \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Hyundai.<\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><b>Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m cho s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd<\/b><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hyundai Venue s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng Kappa 1.0L 3 xilanh t\u0103ng \u00e1p s\u1ea3n sinh ra c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t t\u1ed1i \u0111a 120 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng m\u00f4 men xo\u1eafn c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1t 172 Nm. Xe ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 ly h\u1ee3p k\u00e9p 7 c\u1ea5p. Xe c\u00f3 3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e1i, bao g\u1ed3m Eco ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m, Normal c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 Sport th\u1ec3 thao gi\u00fap b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i khi v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-vanhanh05-3-1710819887992-17108198881331364932033.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 5.\" src=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-vanhanh05-3-1710819887992-17108198881331364932033.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 5.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-vanhanh05-3-1710819887992-17108198881331364932033.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<div id=\"admzone480458\">\n<div id=\"zone-480458\">\n<div id=\"share-jtgyri8j\">\n<div id=\"placement-566503\">\n<div id=\"banner-480458-566503\">\n<div id=\"slot-1-480458-566503\">\n<div id=\"ssppagebid_563\">\n<div id=\"adnzone_516432\" class=\"banner0\" data-ssp=\"sspbid_2010020\" data-admssprqid=\"01c86f9d-5251-4754-8522-967bbd4cbc44141-65fab2bf\" data-location=\"7\" data-width=\"640\" data-height=\"360\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\">\n<div class=\"h-show-pc\">\n<div class=\"c-banner\">\n<div class=\"c-banner-item is-custom-size\">\n<div class=\"c-banner-item__inner\">\n<div class=\"c-banner-item__box\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"h-show-mobile\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<div class=\"c-banner\">\n<div class=\"c-banner-item is-custom-size\">\n<div class=\"c-banner-item__inner\">\n<div class=\"c-banner-item__box\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-noithat05-1-1710819889132-17108198892701225847928.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 6.\" src=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-noithat05-1-1710819889132-17108198892701225847928.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 6.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-noithat05-1-1710819889132-17108198892701225847928.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Hyundai t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0 van c\u1eeda x\u1ea3 (waste-gate) \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u ho\u00e1 d\u00f2ng ch\u1ea3y, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn \u1edf v\u00f2ng tua th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a b\u01b0\u1edbm ga; c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 phun x\u0103ng \u00e1p su\u1ea5t l\u00ean t\u1edbi 200 bar, nh\u1eb1m t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i.\u00a0 \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi 1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 k\u00edch c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hyundai Venue ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n trang b\u1ecb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng an to\u00e0n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 ABS, EBD, BA, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed (ESC), h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh ngang d\u1ed1c (HAC), ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u1ef1c k\u00e9o (TCS), camera l\u00f9i, c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u00e1p su\u1ea5t l\u1ed1p (TPMS). Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n trang b\u1ecb hai t\u00fai kh\u00ed, c\u00f2n phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 6 t\u00fai kh\u00ed.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-noithat05-7-1710819890061-17108198902061144451225.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 7.\" src=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-noithat05-7-1710819890061-17108198902061144451225.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 7.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-noithat05-7-1710819890061-17108198902061144451225.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-noithat05-8-1710819890767-1710819890835703256000.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 8.\" src=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-noithat05-8-1710819890767-1710819890835703256000.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 8.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-noithat05-8-1710819890767-1710819890835703256000.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">V\u1ec1 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh, khi \u1edf \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb, Hyundai Venue t\u1ecf ra l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc xe kh\u00e1 \u201cngoan\u201d, c\u00e1ch \u00e2m t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb v\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfng m\u00e1y hay ti\u1ebfng xe c\u1ed9 di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o cabin d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1ea5m m\u00fat ti\u00eau \u00e2m. V\u00f4-l\u0103ng tr\u1ee3 l\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec7n nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e1i kh\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. Ch\u1ea1y tr\u00ean cao t\u1ed1c, m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ee3 l\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n, khi\u1ebfn tay l\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7m h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Khi di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed3i n\u00fai v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00fac cua g\u1ea5p, m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ed3 gh\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ed5 g\u00e0, xe v\u1eabn v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. Hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eb7n xo\u1eafn khung khi v\u00e0o cua \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau. C\u00e1c c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e1i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e8n b\u00e1o ESC nh\u1ea5p nh\u00e1y ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng an to\u00e0n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u1ed7i khi ch\u00e2n ga h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o cua h\u01a1i gi\u00e0.<\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Do s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1p d\u00e0y 215\/60, xe ch\u1ea1y kh\u00e1 \u00eam d\u00f9 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u1edd g\u1ea7m cao 200 mm, Hyundai Venue v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh x\u1ea5u, offroad nh\u1eb9 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 ly h\u1ee3p k\u00e9p cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ed1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n, gi\u00fap xe v\u1ecdt \u0111i c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n, c\u1ea3m x\u00fac h\u01a1n sau m\u1ed7i c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p ga.<\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Chuy\u1ec3n qua Sport Mode, Venue t\u1ecf ra d\u1eef d\u1eb1n h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. Nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p ga \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng khi chi\u1ebfc xe v\u1ecdt l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 1 kho\u1ea3ng l\u1eb7ng \u201csuy ngh\u0129\u201d r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c di chuy\u1ec3n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y chi\u1ebfc xe kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u00eam n\u1eefa, ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o cabin kh\u00e1 r\u00f5.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-vanhanh05-8-1710819891421-17108198916591626552496.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 9.\" src=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-vanhanh05-8-1710819891421-17108198916591626552496.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed ch\u1ea1y Hyundai Venue: H\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac- \u1ea2nh 9.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cafefcdn.com\/203337114487263232\/2024\/3\/19\/hyundai-venue-vanhanh05-8-1710819891421-17108198916591626552496.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Nh\u1eefng \u00e2m thanh g\u1ea7m g\u1eeb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 m\u1ed7i khi d\u1ed3n s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00f2ng tua t\u1ea1o momen chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng c\u00fa t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i kh\u00e1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch, d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu xe b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u1ee1 A. Ri\u00eang x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e1i, Venue l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh di chuy\u1ec3n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.<\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t \u1edf vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng an to\u00e0n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng Hyundai SmartSense, xong Venue \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc SUV \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u1ee7 d\u00f9ng \u1edf ti\u1ec7n nghi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean ni\u1ec1m vui v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh cho s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hyundai Venue s\u1edf h\u1eefu ngo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh b\u1eaft m\u1eaft th\u1eddi trang, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c vui th\u00fa khi c\u1ea7m l\u00e1i nh\u1edd c\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac Ngo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1 t\u00ednh Tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16\/12\/2023, Hyundai Venue nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15058,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[30],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_w